<text top="1081" left="822" width="10" height="14" font="13"><b>3 </b></text>
<text top="1081" left="90" width="44" height="12" font="14">07-40295 </text>
<text top="1096" left="90" width="3" height="14" font="13"><b> </b></text>
<text top="132" left="90" width="118" height="17" font="3">(<i>spoke in French</i>) </text>
<text top="159" left="90" width="7" height="17" font="3"> </text>
<text top="159" left="126" width="331" height="17" font="3">This statement will be issued as a document of </text>
<text top="177" left="90" width="386" height="17" font="3">the Security Council under the symbol </text>
<text top="195" left="90" width="117" height="17" font="3">S/PRST/2007/23. </text>
